.TH dos2unix 3f
.XI dos2unix - "Convert DOS format files to UNIX format files"
.SH NAME
dos2unix \-  Convert DOS format files to UNIX format files
.Me $a
.SH SYNOPSIS
.na
\fBme\fR "@dos2unix" \fI<files>\fR
.ad
.SH DESCRIPTION
The start-up file \fCdos2unix.emf\fR may be invoked from the command line as a
filter to convert  all files in  \s-1MS-DOS\s0  (or  Windows)  format into the
correct \s-1UNIX\s0 format.
.PP
Each file  specified on the command line is  interrogated  and the line ending
modified to \s-1UNIX\s0.
